title: BABYMETAL - Live Rock am Ring 2024
overview: BABYMETAL's performance at Rock am Ring 2024 was a testament to their unique blend of heavy metal and Japanese pop, captivating a massive audience with their energetic show and infectious music. The setlist spanned their discography, including hits like "Megitsune", "Gimme Chocolate!!", and "Road of Resistance", alongside newer tracks like "BxMxC," and "RATATATA" with Electric Callboy.
